snippet.title: Changing to Amber Electric? Watch this first!
snippet.description:
00:00 - Intro
01:10 - Why switch
04:18 - Amber bills 101
10:38 - Competitor bills
12:30 - Powerwall 2 & Amber
14:30 - Recommendations

SUPPORT
Help support this channel on Patreon. By joining from as little as $2 per month, you early access to news, polls, behind the scenes content, on-air shout-outs, and more. 
https://www.patreon.com/chrisvanderstock

If you’re in the market for a Tesla Model 3, S, or X, consider using my referral code for 1,500 km of free super-charging! https://ts.la/chris39709

SOCIALS
Twitter: @cvanderstock (for my rants and daily musings on random stuff)
Instagram: chris_vanderstock (for the pictures! We're visual creatures)

MUSIC
INOSSI www.soundcloud.com/inossi/
